Random Pie Walker.

This recipe decides which way to go based on the mixing bowl.

Ingredients.
78 g north  # ASCII 'N'
83 g south  # ASCII 'S'
69 g east   # ASCII 'E'
87 g west   # ASCII 'W'
1 g counter

Method.
Take counter from refrigerator.       # Irgendeine Zahl einlesen, um den Tick zu starten
Put north into the mixing bowl.
Put south into the mixing bowl.
Put east into the mixing bowl.
Put west into the mixing bowl.
Mix the mixing bowl well.              # Die Richtungen werden im Bowl-Stack zuf√§llig gemischt
Fold counter into the mixing bowl.     # Nimm die oberste Richtung vom Stack
Liquefy counter.                       # Stelle sie auf "Ausgabe als Zeichen"
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.  # Bereite die Ausgabe vor
Refrigerate.                           // Beende das Programm und gib die Baking dish aus

Serves 1.
